      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the breakdown. i've already checked the scanners and the training seems up to date, so i'm struggling to see where these tiny gaps are coming from. it's not enough to be a major theft issue, but it's just enough to mess up our end-of-month reporting. if it's not theft or a scanning error, what else usually causes these kinds of \"unexplained\" small losses in a high-volume environment like this?",
