      "content": "it's weird because we checked the software sync and the logs look fine. it really feels like stuff is just... vanishing. like it's almost impossible for these specific amounts to just be rounding errors or misplaced items every single week. is there any other psychological or weird systematic reason where things just go missing in these small bursts?",
